{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376030/extras/DMci6d.png?t=1684203530\" /><br><br>Minor Scale is a rhythm-based tower defense game with a 2D / 3D hybrid whimsical aesthetic. You will conduct a band of cute little Critters to defend their jam session from the creepy Crawlies threatening their home with the power of music.<br><br>- Unique combination of rhythm and tower defense mechanics<br>- Place critters to defeat the crawlies by playing along with the music<br>- For lovers of rhythm games, tower defense, and cute creatures<br>- Hit notes to earn crescendo meter<br>- Defeat crawlies to place more critters to earn currency<br>- Original soundtrack<br>- Start your waves on your own time","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Welcome!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2376030/8f0fa507ba371ca439bc9d7e38dde9fa5a850b21.jpg"},{"name":"Beat Level 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2376030/a44abc13c4c81480ee8020bf16e0b69267c41c74.jpg"},{"name":"Beat Level 2","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2376030/d47bef7082d7d8e3e6fa65d0f2bebb890edead5e.jpg"},{"name":"Beat Level 3","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2376030/3943affd3a39a5987aa2a813011a0879966c7610.jpg"},{"name":"Early Grave","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2376030/74e8a0a3f1125216140e86230b138d6e267d12a6.jpg"},{"name":"Suicide Squad","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2376030/32bcec9e8e668657f3f7b0868a9a26ef63b0e45f.jpg"},{"name":"Masochist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2376030/15a45eb4d50a2e0762ec8ab9f337797210723323.jpg"},{"name":"Snuffed Out","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2376030/65257